text: Civil Contract (, , ՔՊ, KP, often shortened to Քաղպայմանագիր, K'aghpaymanagir) is a centrist political party in Armenia. It was created in 2013. They are currently the majority party in the National Assembly. ==References== Category:2013 establishments in Asia Category:Establishments in Armenia Category:Political parties in Armenia Category:Centrist parties
